  "keyFeatures": [
    "Interactive map view with realistic elevation showing nearby payphones",
    "Location-based discovery and navigation to payphones",
    "View claim history and user details for each payphone",
    "Distance calculation from user to payphone locations",
    "Filter payphones by claim status (all/unclaimed)",
